high_descs: Turn and go to the table.
Pick up a butter knife on the table.
Cut a potato on the table.
Turn and go to the counter by the toaster.
Put the knife in the cupboard under the counter.
Turn and go to the table.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn and go to the microwave
Heat the slice of potato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the table.
Put the slice of potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Cut the potato on the white table into slices
Turn around and step forward to face the cabinet to the right of the stove.
Place the knife in the cabinet to the right of the stove.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the white table.
Pick up a slice of potato from on the white table.
Turn right and walk forward and turn to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Take a step to the left and face the white table.
Put the slice of potato on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of potato and place it on the white table.

high_descs: Go to the white table
Pick up the knife
Cut the farther potato
Go to the cabinet between the oven and the fridge
Put the knife in the cabinet
Go to the white table
Pick up a potato slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice
Go to the white table
Put the potato slice down on the table
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato slice on a table
